OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,FSinger songwriter Lois talking to
OL,7,FElaine Willcox at The Bobbin in
OL,8,FLancaster
OL,10,FA singer songwriter from Morecambe has
OL,11,Frevealed bands often get just a #50
OL,12,Fstandard live fee - which has not
OL,13,Fchanged since the 80s.
OL,15,FFor Lois that means she can pay her
OL,16,Fband but there isn't enough to pay
OL,17,Fherself.
OL,19,FShe's campaigning for an increase as
OL,20,Fshe tours with her second EP Seven and
OL,21,Fworks on her first album.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
