PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old says she relies on her
OL,7,Fparents who are often her roadies, who
OL,8,Falso run her merchandise stalls at
OL,9,Fgigs.
OL,11,FShe is going on tour with the Kitchen
OL,12,Fdisco queen in Covid, Sophie Ellis
OL,13,FBextor in the summer, and enjoys
OL,14,Fplaying in bigger venues.
OL,16,FThe 24 year old says performing close
OL,17,Fto home at the Winter Gardens would be
OL,18,Fher dream gig and playing at Six Music
OL,19,FFestival.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
