PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,FLois is an independent artist, who has
OL,7,Fjust finished her first sell out
OL,8,Fheadline tour.
OL,10,F"I just thought, I'm sick of waiting
OL,11,Faround for someone else to just booked
OL,12,Fme, and surely there's a way I can do
OL,13,Fit myself. So with like a few kind of
OL,14,Fconversations and a bit of research, I
OL,15,Fthought I could actually do this and
OL,16,Fhopefully people turn up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,F"Luckily they did. And I just wanted
OL,7,Fto be able to play those songs exactly
OL,8,Fhow they're intended, which is with
OL,9,Fpeople, and to be able to connect with
OL,10,Fan audience and so we did it, and it
OL,11,Fwas amazing."
OL,13,FShe says having her own a band on
OL,14,Fstage, has meant she's grown in
OL,15,Fconfidence on stage.
OL,17,F"That's where I want to be, I love
OL,18,Fperforming live".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,F" My band, they're my best friends.
OL,7,FAnd it's really, really great to be
OL,8,Fable to share the music with them on
OL,9,Fstage, especially with my drummer
OL,10,FFaye."
OL,12,F"I think a lot of the songs are about
OL,13,Fand things that we go through as
OL,14,Fwomen, and I can look to her and she
OL,15,Fjust feels it the way I feel it."
OL,17,FShe was back at The Bobbin pub in
OL,18,FLancaster, which was where she first
OL,19,Fperformed as a teenager.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
