PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,F"I think the first venue I played solo
OL,7,Fat Lancaster Music Festival. Just me
OL,8,Fand a piano Steely Dan T-shirt,"
OL,10,F"It's really special to come back now
OL,11,Fbecause I think about that 18 year old
OL,12,Fwho is here,
OL,14,FLois says she isn't ''waiting for men
OL,15,Fin a boardroom' to make decisions
OL,16,Fabout her career and is taking charge
OL,17,Fherself.
OL,19,FShe's fighting for an increase in the
OL,20,Fstandard live fee, which hasn't
OL,21,Fincreased in decades.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
