PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,F"It's still that famous #50 it hasn't
OL,7,Fchanged. #50 for a full band set as
OL,8,Fwell."
OL,10,F"I don't pay myself anymore because I
OL,11,Fjust can't afford to. I've now got
OL,12,Ffive in the band, instead of four.
OL,14,F"I think the fees been the same since
OL,15,Fthe 80s. So it'd be nice to like,
OL,16,Fraise that to maybe #100 perhaps."
OL,18,F"So we can like pay to get there,
OL,19,Fmaybe get a snack. That would be
OL,20,Fgreat."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
