PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,FFashion is a big part of Lois' stage
OL,7,Fpresence and she designs her own
OL,8,Fmerchandise on sale at her gigs, but
OL,9,Fstill works in a cafe to help support
OL,10,Fher music career.
OL,12,F"I would really, urge bands to have
OL,13,Ftheir own merch and just know that
OL,14,Fyour career isn't in the hands of
OL,15,Fother people."
OL,17,FShe is also a big supporter of women
OL,18,Fin the industry. One of her
OL,19,Fcontemporaries Bria Keely from Better
OL,20,FJoy who is from Cheshire suggested
OL,21,FLois for our introducing series.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
