PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777665953
OL,3,CSinger songwriter Lois reveals bands
OL,4,Cget just #50 a live gig
OL,6,F"I've got a female drummer, a female
OL,7,Fmanager, it's all about the women."
OL,9,F"The fangirls are the basis of the
OL,10,Findustry. If it wasn't for them, the
OL,11,Fartists like Olivia De and Lola and
OL,12,FNivola, they wouldn't be where they
OL,13,Fare. I really think fangirls need to
OL,14,Fget more credit
OL,16,F"They really are the foundation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
